ed.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944630/extras/5d986bcead1322d1b284c8a8ff6bbbc2.webm?t=1727864387\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1944630/extras/5d986bcead1322d1b284c8a8ff6bbbc2.mp4?t=1727864387\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
